## Database Design Principles

### Users Table
- Central authentication table with bcrypt password hashing
- Tracks user preferences (learning_style, skill_level)
- Maintains activity timestamps for analytics

### Progress Tracking
- Denormalized progress data for fast queries
- Session-based tracking with start/end timestamps
- Supports both course-level and concept-level progress

### Knowledge Graph (Neo4j)
- Concepts as nodes with metadata
- PREREQUISITE relationships for learning paths
- RELATED_TO connections for cross-topic exploration
